data.description: Experience the perfect blend of timeless charm and modern luxury in this exquisitely remodeled Antique-Colonial style home. With 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a 2-car garage. Step inside to discover two spacious family areas with cozy fireplaces and majestic live-wood-edge mantles, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. The open concept kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring modern elements, ample storage, and high-quality stainless steel appliances. The master suite offers a private oasis with a walk-in closet and a luxurious washroom boasting a full-tiled roman shower and a overhead rain fixture. The second bedroom is equally impressive, with double walk-through closets and access to a full bath. Outside, the privacy-fenced backyard is a haven for relaxation and entertainment, featuring a well maintained lawn and patio with built-in monitor, sound, and light systems. Don't miss out on this meticulously renovated home that perfectly combines classic charm with modern elegance.
